headline: OATI deploys FERC Order 881 compliance solution with six transmission providers
summary: In a demonstration of OATI's scale and effectiveness within the energy industry, six transmission providers in North America have successfully deployed OATI's solution for ambient-adjusted ratings (AAR) to comply with FERC Order 881.
